{
  "stem": "5911.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jews-- but also with-- with-- with Germans, I mean, Germans-- no Lithuanians anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--at labor camps, we had Germans-- Germans-- German soldiers, German police.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were watching us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But again, we were very happy to leave Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was very afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She had this sixth sense and luck that-- can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That again-- [LAUGHS] Did you fall ill at all--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was OK too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were-- by the end of '44, we were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because don't forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to march from every camp to the other one, we marched.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now my mother says, and she's 100% right, that she did save my life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because in-- during the marches, she kept on pushing me, not to fall down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you fell down, you were finished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she says she remembers-- I don't remember as well-- mothers cuddling their children, their daughters-- not children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They weren't children-- like daughters-- cuddling their daughters, and not being very strong emotionally to push them on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother pushed me on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she also tells of a story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe she'll be able to tell it to you herself-- taking my shoes and putting in her bosom to warm them up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But she kept on pushing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was very short, but a dynamite.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In-- in Russian they used to call her [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She was always in charge-- always.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe in Stutthof-- maybe in Stutthof-- not in the labor camps, because they wouldn't take you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You would have been killed-- maybe in Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the ghetto there was a lot of babies born in the ghetto, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't remember about Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the cold months.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the work, and people dying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
